      <title>汽车制造商马鲁蒂铃木销量增加，利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/carmaker-maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-on-higher-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的汽车制造商玛鲁蒂铃木印度有限公司公布季度利润好于预期，主要由于运动型多功能车带动销量增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/carmaker-maruti-suzuki-beats-profit-forecast-on-higher-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 10:27:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
