      <title>由于溃败侵蚀投资回报，中国人寿利润下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/china-life-profit-falls-as-stocks-rout-erodes-investment-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场份额最大的人寿保险公司中国人寿表示，由于股票投资下降和债券收益率下降削弱了回报，第一季度利润下降了9.3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/china-life-profit-falls-as-stocks-rout-erodes-investment-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 10:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
